## Smart lighting is helpful lighting
With Google Home, your smart lighting can do more, including helping you to sleep better, feel safer, and more.

### Benefits of Smart Lighting
* Sleep better
* Feel safer
* Save time
* Save energy

## Light the way to better sleep and wellness
Fall asleep more easily and wake up refreshed with Gentle Sleep & Wake. At night, let Google gradually dim your lights, adjusting the hues to lull you into a restful sleep. In the morning, ease into the day with lights that mimic the sunrise.
### Gentle Sleep and Wake
* Learn more

## Feel safer with lights that know when it’s dark
Create custom Routines to turn your lights on at sunset and back off at sunrise so you can feel safer year round – automatically.
### Sunset and Sunrise Routines
* Learn more

## Let your home help when you’re in a hurry
Save precious minutes when you’re rushing out the door with Home & Away Routines. With presence sensing, your Away Routine can turn off lights, turn on cameras, and set your thermostat to Eco mode when you leave.
### Home and Away Routines
* Learn more

## Save energy without thinking twice
Save energy throughout your entire home – even if you forget to flip the switch. Create a custom Routine to turn off lights and other devices at a specific time or with a simple voice command.
### Energy-Saving Routines
* Learn more

