## Requirements and Notes
1. Requires working internet and Wi-Fi.
2. If your device doesn't support color, lights will still brighten and dim.
3. Home Routines require additional enrollment and setup, and depend on working internet, Wi-Fi and service availability from Google, and third parties that manufacture devices included in the Routines.
4. Remote control and mobile notifications require working internet and Wi-Fi.

